##Lost in Translation: After 15 days of wandering straight to Wenzhou, I finally got off the highway, but..

WECHAT goodlife225

Functional Introduction, the relentless years, there is love.

This Spring Festival is a bit awkward

Dictation / boss Chen

(manager of a restaurant in Wenzhou)
I didn't sleep last night. I set off this morning. I want to go back to big Wenzhou.

But it's been driving all day, and it's 6:00 at night, and I'm still stuttering on the North Yueqing highway, eating a waffle.

This is my Lantern Festival dinner.

Plus today, I've been living in my car for 15 days, munching on instant noodles until I have canker sores.

I am in the Mount Sanqing service area

I am from Anhui, doing business in Wenzhou, my ID card address is Sichuan, years ago I went to Shangrao, Jiangxi to see friends.

Then, because of the road closures, I couldn't go anywhere.

My clothes were all dirty and wet, and my car had only two compartments of oil left.

I don't want to go anywhere else, I just want to go back to my big Wenzhou.

But after a long day, I'm still on the road, I still can't get home..

01
Suddenly I'm pissed, but I just want to go home

The last few days in Mount Sanqing, I've actually been trying to figure out.

I post on my facebook page every day, and I find myself getting annoyed by groups of people saying the same thing about me as Xuanzang.

Yesterday I told my story to a friend who wrote about it online to see if she could get help.

My phone's been ringing off the hook since 10:00 p.m. The employee says, "manager, you're trending. "

The power of the Internet is just too great.

I was wearing a mask. Everyone who saw me recognized me. Some even said my mask was on backwards.

I used to be a bit of a celebrity in Wenzhou, the restaurant scene in our town, but this is the most famous.

I didn't want to be so famous. Besides, why can't I go back to Wenzhou? Somebody help me?

I've been up since 7:00 in the morning. Actually, I've been up most of the night.

Some of the netizens felt sorry for me and some scolded me.

I've been thinking about it all night. I'm a book.

UPS and downs. I've been through a lot. I've been hit by a car twice, I've been flooded twice, I've been quarantined for dengue... you can count on me to get back on my feet!

In fact, AH, said I was the boss, actually just a small businessman, I still rent a house in Wenzhou, 1,500 yuan a month. I wasn't lying when I said I didn't have any money for gas. I've lost a lot of business this year.

After setting off, I went to the Qingtian Service station first

I packed my car this morning, and I'm ready to go.

I am a clean person, these days all eat and drink in the car, too dirty.

My friends gave me some money yesterday. I think I have enough gas. Thank you.

It's after 9:00. I'm off.

Bye, Mount Sanqing Service. Bye, big brother.

02
Wenzhou expressway so many, which one will open for me?

Wenzhou has several highway junctions, I intend to go to the port of Seven Mile Highway Junction, no longer go to the Yueqing entrance, Wenzhou East, Wenzhou South..

Drink a can of coffee and try them one at a time. Go!

Wenzhou direction, along the way in addition to a few trucks, a car only one of me.

"What is this place, is still so desolate, that Owari Naki Tabi, so long, I am always toward the distant lonely wanderer. " Too Lonely, I played a song, just Xu Wei, listening to a little bit want to cry.

I took a short break in the Qingtian Service area, and there were no shops open here.

I have low blood sugar, my head is a little dizzy, and I'm shaking.

I had some more coffee.

My friend showed me a message, and I wasn't feeling well.

That message said, three back personnel must not take the luck psychology before March 1 back to Wenzhou, back to self-financed isolation, a day 800.

I'm back on the road. What if it's still free, or just a little bit?

I was at port seven again

At 15:07, I arrived at the Qiligang Expressway junction in Wenzhou. This place is completely blocked off.

I'm GONNA pull over and go get the crew. They said, "try North Yueqing. There's no way through. " .
One of the town leaders called me, told me not to worry, to try again, she also tried to help me find out.

At 15:55, I got to the North Yueqing highway, and sure enough, it was blocked again.

Really Tired, I ran to the duty of the special police, do not have a way? 'You have to have a pass, ' he said. 'Let the community or the company do it. '.

I called 110,12345, all kinds of friends. It's making my head spin.

The result is that this kind of pass is very difficult to do out, generally only during the epidemic period of some special industries can be done, our catering industry does not fall into this category.

I don't have a house in Wenzhou, nor do I know the leaders of the villages where I rent.

Right now, I'm still parked at the North Wenzhou expressway entrance.

It was dark again, and another day was drawing to a close.

I ate some Wangwang snow cakes

There's a couple of wafers in the car. I'll eat them and figure it out.

Maybe in the car today. What about tomorrow?

03
I finally got off the highway, but..

Another friend said that the East Wenzhou Expressway has been restored.

I'll try again. Worst case, I have big brother.

At 19:13, I arrived in East Wenzhou. There's really no seal!

The rest of the way!

I got a little worked up when they pulled me over.

They checked my ID card, took my temperature, and I took out the health certificate from the Health Center.

They didn't say anything. My Car's GONNA make it!

We made it through!

But friends say Yueqing is closed. If I can get into Wenzhou, I may not get into Yueqing.

Sure enough, I got off the highway, to the Ouyue bridge entrance was stopped, the traffic police saw my identity card, advised me to return, I said I really can not move, I have been in the highway and car for 15 days, my heart beat faster.

I showed the traffic police the certificate issued by Shangrao Hospital in Jiangxi, and the traffic police let me pass.

I crossed the bridge, another jam, and I was stopped again. The traffic police here still advised me to return, I said I really can not go, I go where AH, Jiangxi is not my home, I just go to see a friend, Sichuan so far.

I said I was tired and my heart was racing.

A traffic policeman listened to my story, made a phone call, then came over and let me sit for a while, he made me a bowl of instant noodles, another traffic policeman brought me oranges. After eating instant noodles and oranges, I feel refreshed.

They said I could be picked up by the shareholders of the hotel, but the shareholders of my hotel are not in Wenzhou.

The traffic cop went to make another phone call and came up to me and said, "tonight, you're going to have a hard time. Tomorrow we'll try to get you back to Yueqing. " 

Now, my heart should be able to put it down! ?

Thanks to all my friends who always care about me!
